OL,3,CGreat British Energy board to meet for
OL,4,Cfirst time in Scotland
OL,6,FThe board of a publicly-owned clean
OL,7,Fenergy company set up by the UK Labour
OL,8,FGovernment is scheduled to meet for
OL,9,Fthe first time in Scotland on Monday
OL,10,Fto discuss scaling up and kickstarting
OL,11,Finvestments.
OL,13,FEnergy minister Michael Shanks will
OL,14,Fconvene the meeting of the Great
OL,15,FBritish Energy start-up board in
OL,16,FAberdeen alongside chairman Juergen
OL,17,FMaier and interim chief executive Dan
OL,18,FMcGrail to discuss next steps for the
OL,19,Forganisation.
