OL,3,CGreat British Energy board to meet for
OL,4,Cfirst time in Scotland
OL,6,FIt is expected the discussions will
OL,7,Finvolve building up an investment
OL,8,Fportfolio which members hope will
OL,9,Freturn a profit for taxpayers.
OL,11,FGreat British Energy has already
OL,12,Fstarted engaging with the market on
OL,13,Fpotential collaborations to ensure it
OL,14,Fcan deliver benefits for the public
OL,15,Fonce it is fully established, backed
OL,16,Fby #8.3 billion over the course of the
OL,17,Fcurrent Parliament.
