OL,3,CGreat British Energy board to meet for
OL,4,Cfirst time in Scotland
OL,6,FMr Shanks said: "We now have a
OL,7,Ffantastic team in place to lead Great
OL,8,FBritish Energy and establish the
OL,9,Fcompany in Aberdeen.
OL,11,F"By unlocking homegrown clean power
OL,12,Fprojects, Great British Energy will
OL,13,Fsupport thousands of well-paid jobs in
OL,14,FScotland and across the country, and
OL,15,Fdeliver energy security for the
OL,16,FBritish people.
OL,18,F"Today's meeting of the new board
OL,19,Fmembers marks another step forward for
OL,20,Fthe company as it gears up to make its
OL,21,Ffirst investments."
