OL,3,CGreat British Energy board to meet for
OL,4,Cfirst time in Scotland
OL,6,FMr Maier said: "We are working on a
OL,7,Fplan to invest in and deliver
OL,8,Fhomegrown clean power, supporting the
OL,9,Fnext generation of energy jobs.
OL,11,F"We are already engaging with industry
OL,12,Fon exciting investment opportunities
OL,13,Fso we can hit the ground running once
OL,14,FGreat British Energy is fully
OL,15,Festablished.
OL,17,F"Together we will back British
OL,18,Finnovation and support the creation of
OL,19,Fthousands of jobs in clean energy
OL,20,Fprojects and their supply chains in
OL,21,Fthe North East of Scotland alone."
