OL,3,CGreat British Energy board to meet for
OL,4,Cfirst time in Scotland
OL,6,FMr McGrail said: "Great British Energy
OL,7,Fis perfectly placed to take advantage
OL,8,Fof the clean energy revolution for the
OL,9,Fbenefit of the British people.
OL,11,F"As I take up post as interim CEO
OL,12,Ftoday, I'm pleased to bring our new
OL,13,Fboard members together in Aberdeen to
OL,14,Fdiscuss our plans to invest in secure,
OL,15,Fhomegrown clean power ` unleashing
OL,16,Fjobs and crowding in private
OL,17,Finvestment."
