OL,6,FMr Maier is also expected to convene a
OL,7,Fskills roundtable on Tuesday to work
OL,8,Fwith industry to help oil and gas
OL,9,Fworkers in north-east Scotland access
OL,10,Fclean energy jobs.
OL,12,FIt is scheduled to be attended by
OL,13,Forganisations including Skills
OL,14,FDevelopment Scotland, the Scottish
OL,15,FTrades Union Congress, Green Free
OL,16,FPorts Cromarty and Leith, ETZ Ltd, and
OL,17,FAberdeen and Grampian Chambers of
OL,18,FCommerce.
